    <h3>Option B: Deck Oven (For Bread-Focused Bakeries)</h3>
    <p>If bread is your core product — sourdough, baguettes, pav, whole wheat loaves — a deck oven with steam injection is essential. The stone deck provides radiant bottom heat that convection can't replicate. For a 500 sq ft bakery, a 2-deck oven is the sweet spot between capacity and footprint.</p>

